race.description: Thank You Blue Spec Drilling Handicap
race.comment: ZING TO WIN (2) has been racing well without winning and placed last time in stronger. Maps well and Faithful sticks aboard. Finds the right race and can return to the winners' circle. Stablemate TREASURED QUEEN (4) rates similarly on his near miss in a 64 when he led. The in-form Fiore replaces the 3kg apprentice and she can threaten. SURE THING (3) has been disappointing since the first-up win this grade, but finally draws an inside barrier, which he will use. Has the ability and a better effort is likely. PEARLY NUGGETT (1) delivered the hat trick beating TREASURED QUEEN home. Has top weight but the form is hard to knock. BAALBEK (5) is thrown in with the 3kg claim and is a hope forgiving the latest.
